casebody.data:
Rupert E. BAPTISTE, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Fatou A. JALLOW-BAPTISTE, n/k/a Fatou A. Jallow, Defendant. M-1092/1093 September Term 2017
079394 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-1092) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-1093) is denied.
